title: Side Chair, ca. 1780
creditline: Bequest of Mrs. John Innes Kane
description: Three, curvilinear-shaped splats characterize back.  Upper posts are tapered.  Two lateral and two longitudinal stretchers.  Upholstered seat (light pink).
